  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is a multi-center, double blind, parallel group placebo controlled randomised trial
      designed to determine the safety and efficacy of a Standardised Extract of Phyllanthus
      Niruri (EPN 797) HEPAR-P capsule for the treatment of Non-alcoholic Fatty Liver Disease for
      a treatment period of 48 weeks
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
